---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Cookie Policy">
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-16">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">Cookie Policy</h1>
    <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none space-y-6 text-[#94a3b8]">
      <p><strong class="text-[#e2e8f0]">Last updated:</strong> May 2026</p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#e2e8f0] mt-8">What Are Cookies</h2>
      <p>Cookies are small text files stored on your device when you visit a website. They help us provide you with a better experience.</p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#e2e8f0] mt-8">How We Use Cookies</h2>
      <p>We use cookies for:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
        <li>Essential website functionality</li>
        <li>Analytics to understand how visitors use our site</li>
        <li>Advertising to serve relevant ads</li>
        <li>Remembering your preferences</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#e2e8f0] mt-8">Types of Cookies</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
        <li><strong class="text-[#e2e8f0]">Session cookies:</strong> Temporary cookies that expire when you close your browser</li>
        <li><strong class="text-[#e2e8f0]">Persistent cookies:</strong> Remain on your device until they expire or you delete them</li>
        <li><strong class="text-[#e2e8f0]">Third-party cookies:</strong> Set by our analytics and advertising partners</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#e2e8f0] mt-8">Managing Cookies</h2>
      <p>You can control cookies through your browser settings. Note that disabling cookies may affect website functionality.</p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#e2e8f0] mt-8">Third-Party Cookies</h2>
      <p>We use Google Analytics and Google AdSense, which may set their own cookies. Please refer to their respective privacy policies for more information.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
